snippet.title: Tesla Simulator - A dream for Tesla fans!
snippet.description:
The Tesla Simulator is an unofficial simulation developed by just one person. It's maybe not the best looking game, but it has great physics and driving around and exploring the map is pure fun.
You can drive every Tesla car which is available at the moment plus the Roadster 2. Generation and the Tesla Semi.
There are several places to explore. There is a parking lot with superchargers in front of a mini Tesla factory, the Tesla test track and multiple Falcon 9 rockets spread over the map.

Download the Tesla Simulator here:
https://www.habrador.com/p/tesla-simulator/
